            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>Our mission is to provide students with a seamless and efficient way to access and manage laptops, ensuring that their academic journey is smooth and uninterrupted. The Digital Library system offers a platform where students can easily see the availability of laptops, note down their learning points, and manage their tasks effectively.</p>
            <h2>Features</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Real-time updates on laptop availability: Free, Allotted, and Emergency statuses.</li>
                <li>Personalized dashboard for students to keep track of their notes and academic progress.</li>
                <li>Secure login system ensuring the privacy and security of student information.</li>
                <li>User-friendly interface for easy navigation and management.</li>
            </ul>
            <h2>How It Helps Students</h2>
            <p>With the Digital Library, students no longer need to worry about the availability of laptops. They can log in to their accounts and check the status of the laptops at any time. This system also allows them to jot down important learning points and notes, which they can refer to anytime, making it easier to keep track of their academic progress and enhance their learning experience.</p>
